'''安格拉核電廠'''，是巴西唯一的一座核能發電廠。該座電廠位於[[里約熱內盧州|里約熱內盧州]]的{{link-pt|安格拉多斯黑斯|Angra dos Reis}}的 '''Central Nuclear Almirante Álvaro Alberto''' ('''CNAAA''') 。其包含了兩座[[壓水反應爐|壓水反應爐]]，首先在1985年啟用的'''安格拉一號'''的淨輸出為657兆瓦<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eletronuclear.gov.br/perguntas_respostas/perguntas_respostas.php?id_categoria=1&id_subcategoria=2 |title=Eletronuclear - Eletrobrás Termonuclear S.A. - Pronta Resposta<!--  Bot generated title --> |access-date=2010-02-21 |archive-date=2008-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080605175018/http://www.eletronuclear.gov.br/perguntas_respostas/perguntas_respostas.php?id_categoria=1&id_subcategoria=2 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，而'''安格拉二號'''在2000年啟用，淨輸出1,350兆瓦<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eletronuclear.gov.br/perguntas_respostas/perguntas_respostas.php?id_categoria=2&id_subcategoria=5 |title=Eletronuclear - Eletrobrás Termonuclear S.A. - Pronta Resposta<!--  Bot generated title --> |access-date=2010-02-21 |archive-date=2011-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706155900/http://www.eletronuclear.gov.br/perguntas_respostas/perguntas_respostas.php?id_categoria=2&id_subcategoria=5 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。而尚未啟用的'''安格拉三號'''則計畫輸出1,350兆瓦的電力<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eletronuclear.gov.br/perguntas_respostas/perguntas_respostas.php?id_categoria=3&id_subcategoria=7 |title=Eletronuclear - Eletrobrás Termonuclear S.A. - Pronta Resposta<!--  Bot generated title --> |access-date=2010-02-21 |archive-date=2011-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706155913/http://www.eletronuclear.gov.br/perguntas_respostas/perguntas_respostas.php?id_categoria=3&id_subcategoria=7 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

